Options:

--username=
    The username associated with your OpenStack account.
--apikey=
    Your API key.
--projectid=
    Your Project ID.
--url=
    The API endpoint of your OpenStack implementation.
--model=
    Which FailureModel you wish to use. Current choices are "random", "network_outage", "kill_processes"
--servers=
    A json file with information about the servers, only required for kill_processes, since it will hold information about the layout of the server graph. Could be replaced with metadata in the future.
--repeat=
    How many times to repeat any particular failure model.
--tag=
    A metadata tag that is set on the servers to be used. When creating them, it should be "Anarcho=1", and when executing "--tag=Anarcho"

